I notice you said their guild sold spells, so they are not against magician's and others getting those spells, but they want us to pay homage, and beg them to take our plat, so we can get our spells?<br>
<br>
What is wrong with this picture, and if the answer make the spells no drop, and that would be the end of the game as far as I am concerned.<br>
<br>
Casters play to get their new spells, it is what makes the game fun. Now we raid to get those great new robe, the clicky effects, the stats and hit points of those uber drop, just as melee do, but spells are our bread and butter.<br>
<br>
Could you imagine being in PoP without the new nuke Talons?<br>
