<br>
Take away my spells, and make them off boss mobs, I can't kill because that is where the spells are, and I need them to kill it. Ohh that's right the uber ZERG raid force of 60+ in the top tier guild will rush in and kill the mob, than those mages will have the spell, but no one else till they rape you over the coals for 50,000pp plus.<br>
<br>
Bull I say, you get the Uber Robe01, the Uber02 clicky item, you wear your gloves of Dark Summoning, and out pops a pet better than mine, and you want to take away our spells, because they are worthless. Please don't even go there. it is a lie, and you know it, or destroy them if they do nothing. Of course they do something.<br>
<br>
Sorry Cyrius your wrong on this, very wrong.<br>
<br>
You get your rewards for being in the top tier guild. LOOK at your equipement, and tell me it doesn't make a difference, and if you say it, than don't loot another thing, because it won't matter. IT DOES, you know it, I know it, and everyone on this board knows it. Get off the soap box of trying to deny your fellow magician their spells, because your guild can't make another MILLION PLAT.<br>
